<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜看着其它二年级的孩子们跑出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的父母来接他们了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，尼娜的妈妈很晚才下班。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，尼娜要去儿童中心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜走进体育馆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想回家，在后院玩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42011</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>窗户上一个大横幅写着 “课后活动和游戏，就在儿童中心！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜没有看到认识的人。她很紧张。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我的名字在那儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜发现了自己的名签。她坐下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪来到儿童中心，非常兴奋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，她的名签写错了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉莎贝尔？” 莉琪说，“我叫莉琪，不叫莉莎贝尔！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪看着旁边的男生。“你是贾森吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“欢迎大家！请找到自己的座位。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师是儿童中心的老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜觉得她的笑容很好看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们要装饰名签。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个高高的男生坐在尼娜旁边。他没有打招呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的名签上写着 “波比” 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看一下桌子上的杂志。剪出你喜欢的图片。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132550</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“举个例子。尼娜，你喜欢什么？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜笑了。“我喜欢紫色，还喜欢我的雨靴。” 她害羞地回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好！贾森，你喜欢什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师等了等，“贾森？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪提醒贾森。“他喜欢玩儿电子游戏。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森，我们不在儿童中心玩儿电子游戏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>请收起来。” 雪莉老师严肃地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“除了电子游戏，你还喜欢什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森抬起头。“芝士汉堡。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好！开始剪吧！” 雪莉老师指了指杂志。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请把那本杂志递给我。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请把剪刀递给我。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪挥了挥手。“雪莉老师？我需要一个新名签。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有我奶奶才叫我莉莎贝尔。大家都叫我莉琪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抱歉！你可以做一个新的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师给了她一些硬纸片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在上面打两个孔。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪打了孔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后写上你的名字。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在把你们剪的图片拿出来。把它们粘在名签上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们可以粘在前面或后面，或者两面都粘。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260943</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“做好以后，选一条线，把它穿进孔里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260943</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看！你的名签就变成了一条项链！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师把她的名签戴在脖子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你还可以把它挂在房间的门把上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尼娜，你妈妈来了。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜很惊讶。“活动已经结束了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对呀，该回家了。” 妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再见，雪莉老师！” 尼娜跑向妈妈，“看我的名签！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>